  title: 'Switch Health Insurance in Switzerland (2026) | Change & Save Before Deadlines',
  description: 'Change your Swiss health insurance for 2026. Supplementary: cancel by 30 September. Basic: switch until 30 November. Save up to CHF 2,000/year. Get 3 tailored offers or book a free consultation today.',
